{"id":"api/common/CurrencyPipe","title":"CurrencyPipe","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common/CurrencyPipe\", \"name\": \"CurrencyPipe\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L222-L367\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L222-L367\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"currencypipe\">CurrencyPipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#currencypipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label pipe\">pipe</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">將數字轉換為貨幣字串，根據確定組大小和分隔符、小數點字元和其他特定於區域設定的配置的區域設定規則進行格式化。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Transforms a number to a currency string, formatted according to locale rules\nthat determine group sizing and separator, decimal-point character,\nand other locale-specific configurations.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"pipe-overview\">\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">{{ value_expression | <span class=\"kwd nocode\"><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a></span> [ : currencyCode [ : display [ : digitsInfo [ : locale ] ] ] ] }}</code-example>\n\n  \n<h2 id=\"匯出自\">匯出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#匯出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">CommonModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  <h2 id=\"input-value\">輸入值<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#input-value\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table pipe-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>value</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string | number</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">要格式化為貨幣的數字。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The number to be formatted as currency.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h2 id=\"parameters\">引數<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#parameters\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table pipe-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>currencyCode</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">可選值。預設值為 <code>this._defaultCurrencyCode</code>。</p><p translation-result=\"on\">可選值。預設值為 <code>this._defaultCurrencyCode</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\">ISO 4217</a> currency code,\nsuch as <code>USD</code> for the US dollar and <code>EUR</code> for the euro. The default currency code can be\nconfigured using the <code><a href=\"api/core/DEFAULT_CURRENCY_CODE\" class=\"code-anchor\">DEFAULT_CURRENCY_CODE</a></code> injection token.</p>\n\n\n        \n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>display</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string | boolean</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">貨幣指示器的格式。以下之一：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The format for the currency indicator. One of the following:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>code</code>：顯示程式碼（例如 <code>USD</code>）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>code</code>: Show the code (such as <code>USD</code>).</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>symbol</code>（預設）：顯示符號（例如 <code>$</code>）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>symbol</code>(default): Show the symbol (such as <code>$</code>).</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>symbol-narrow</code>：對有兩個貨幣符號的區域設定使用窄符號。例如，加元 CAD 的符號是 <code>CA$</code> 和符號-narrow <code>$</code>。如果此區域設定沒有窄符號，則使用此區域設定的標準符號。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>symbol-narrow</code>: Use the narrow symbol for locales that have two symbols for their\ncurrency.\nFor example, the Canadian dollar CAD has the symbol <code>CA$</code> and the symbol-narrow <code>$</code>. If the\nlocale has no narrow symbol, uses the standard symbol for the locale.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">字串：使用給定的字串值，而不是程式碼或符號。例如，空字串將抑制貨幣 &amp; 符號。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">String: Use the given string value instead of a code or a symbol.\nFor example, an empty string will suppress the currency &amp; symbol.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">布林值（在 v5 中標記為已棄用）：symbol 為 <code>true</code>，<code>code</code> 為 false。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Boolean (marked deprecated in v5): <code>true</code> for symbol and false for <code>code</code>.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n        <p>可選值。預設值為 <code>'symbol'</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>digitsInfo</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">十進位制表示選項，由以下格式的字串指定：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Decimal representation options, specified by a string\nin the following format:<br>\n<code>{minIntegerDigits}.{minFractionDigits}-{maxFractionDigits}</code>.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>minIntegerDigits</code>：小數點前的最小整數位數。預設為 <code>1</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>minIntegerDigits</code>: The minimum number of integer digits before the decimal point.\nDefault is <code>1</code>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>minFractionDigits</code>：小數點後的最小位數。預設為 <code>2</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>minFractionDigits</code>: The minimum number of digits after the decimal point.\nDefault is <code>2</code>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>maxFractionDigits</code>：小數點後的最大位數。預設為 <code>2</code>。如果未提供，則該數字將根據<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\">ISO 4217</a>指定的內容使用適當的位數格式化。例如，加元有 2 位，而智利比索沒有。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>maxFractionDigits</code>: The maximum number of digits after the decimal point.\nDefault is <code>2</code>.\nIf not provided, the number will be formatted with the proper amount of digits,\ndepending on what the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\">ISO 4217</a> specifies.\nFor example, the Canadian dollar has 2 digits, whereas the Chilean peso has none.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n        <p>可選值。預設值為 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>locale</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">可選值。預設值為 <code>undefined</code>。</p><p translation-result=\"on\">可選值。預設值為 <code>undefined</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A locale code for the locale format rules to use.\nWhen not supplied, uses the value of <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code>, which is <code>en-US</code> by default.\nSee <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\">Setting your app locale</a>.</p>\n\n\n        \n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n</section>\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/common/getCurrencySymbol\" class=\"code-anchor\">getCurrencySymbol</a>()</code></p></li>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/common/formatCurrency\" class=\"code-anchor\">formatCurrency</a>()</code></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">以下程式碼顯示了管道如何根據各種格式規範將數字轉換為文字字串，其中呼叫者的預設區域設定是 <code>en-US</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following code shows how the pipe transforms numbers\ninto text strings, according to various format specifications,\nwhere the caller's default locale is <code>en-US</code>.</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"common/pipes/ts/currency_pipe.ts\" region=\"CurrencyPipe\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'currency-pipe',\n  template: `&lt;div&gt;\n    &lt;!--output '$0.26'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;A: {{a | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output 'CA$0.26'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;A: {{a | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>:'CAD'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output 'CAD0.26'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;A: {{a | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>:'CAD':'code'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output 'CA$0,001.35'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{b | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>:'CAD':'symbol':'4.2-2'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output '$0,001.35'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{b | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>:'CAD':'symbol-narrow':'4.2-2'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output '0&nbsp;001,35&nbsp;CA$'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{b | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>:'CAD':'symbol':'4.2-2':'fr'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output 'CLP1' because CLP has no cents--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{b | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a>:'CLP'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;`\n})\nexport class CurrencyPipeComponent {\n  a: number = 0.259;\n  b: number = 1.3495;\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/formatCurrency\n - api/core/PipeTransform\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/pipes-overview\n - guide/pipes-transform-data\n - start/start-data\n - start/start-forms\n - start/start-routing\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#currencypipe\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#input-value\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#parameters\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#see-also\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#usage-notes\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#匯出自\n - api/common/formatCurrency\n - api/common/getCurrencySymbol\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/DEFAULT_CURRENCY_CODE\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L222-L367\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L222-L367\n-->"}